Vrst (rst 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[ 0n 0.9 12n 0.9 12.1n 0 90n 0 ]
Vclk (clk 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[ 0n 0 4.9n 0 5.0n 0.9 5.5n 0.9 5.6n 0 24.9n 0 25.0n 0.9 25.5n 0.9 25.6n 0 44.9n 0 45.0n 0.9 45.5n 0.9 45.6n 0 64.9n 0 65.0n 0.9 65.5n 0.9 65.6n 0 84.9n 0 85.0n 0.9 85.5n 0.9 85.6n 0 90n 0 ]

XDUT (vin clk mode rst out metric) final_step_edge_counter_file

tran tran stop=90n
save vin clk mode rst out metric
